WinBolo — a faithful reimplementation of Stuart Cheshire's Bolo by John Morrison.
Source: WinBolo (https://github.com/kippandrew/WinBolo / code.google.com/archive/p/winbolo).
Licensed under the GNU General Public License v2 (see LICENSE / gnu.txt).

This is a clean-room reimplementation with its OWN graphics/sounds (GPL) — it does
NOT use Stuart Cheshire's original proprietary assets. This browser build was
compiled to WebAssembly via Emscripten (single-player preview; networked
multiplayer and mouse-driven building are in progress). The repository's top-level
MIT license does not apply to this GPL component.
